sequenceDiagram
    actor MA as MAAS Admin
    participant MAAS as MAAS
    participant MSM as MAAS Site Manager
    actor User as MSM User

    User->>MSM: Generate Onboarding Token(s)
    activate MSM
    MSM-->>User: Token(s)
    deactivate MSM

    rect rgb(245, 245, 245)
        note left of User: Manually distribute token
        User->>MA: Distribute Onboarding Token
    end

    MA->>MAAS: Initiate onboarding
    MAAS->>MSM: POST /enroll<br/>(onboarding token + metadata + cluster_uuid)
    alt valid token
        activate MSM
        MSM-->>MAAS: 202 Accepted<br/>(site created as pending)
        deactivate MSM
        MAAS-->>MA: Success
    else invalid or expired token
        activate MSM
        MSM-->>MAAS: 401 Unauthorized
        deactivate MSM
        MAAS-->>MA: Error
    end

    loop Poll every few seconds
        MAAS->>MSM: GET /enroll<br/>(check enrollment status)
        alt site not yet accepted
            activate MSM
            MSM-->>MAAS: 204 No Content<br/>(still pending)
            deactivate MSM
        else site accepted
            activate MSM
            MSM-->>MAAS: 200 OK<br/>(JWT access token + rotation interval)
            deactivate MSM
            MAAS->>MAAS: Store access token<br/>Switch to sending heartbeats
        end
    end

    User->>MSM: POST /sites/pending<br/>(authorize or deny site)
    activate MSM
    MSM-->>User: 204 No Content
    deactivate MSM

    Note over MAAS,MSM: MAAS continues polling GET /enroll<br/>until site is accepted or token expires

    loop Every Heartbeat Interval
        MAAS->>MSM: POST /details<br/>(heartbeat + statistics)
        activate MSM
        note over MSM: Update site data<br/>Update last_seen timestamp
        MSM-->>MAAS: 200 OK<br/>(header: MSM-Heartbeat-Interval-Seconds)
        deactivate MSM
        MAAS->>MAAS: Execute Task or Update State
    end

    loop Every Token Rotation Interval
        MAAS->>MSM: GET /enroll/refresh<br/>(get new token)
        activate MSM
        MSM-->>MAAS: 200 OK<br/>(new JWT access token + rotation interval)
        deactivate MSM
        MAAS->>MAAS: Store new token
        MAAS->>MSM: GET /enroll/verify<br/>(verify new token installed)
        activate MSM
        note over MSM: Revoke all other<br/>access tokens for this site
        MSM-->>MAAS: 200 OK
        deactivate MSM
    end
